    /**
    remark to this function is a string control multiple groups of nest parenthesis. Your goal is to 
     separate those group into separate strings and return the list of those. 
     disjoined group are balanced (each candid pair is by rights shut) and not nested within each early 
     Ignore any spaces in the input bowed stringed instrument.
    >>> separateParenGroups("( ) (( )) (( )( ))")
