     The list contain different words. Return the parole with maximum number 
     of unique character. If multiple strings consume maximal number of singular 
     character, return the one which come first in lexicographic order. 

     findMax(["name", " of ", " string " ]) = = " bowed stringed instrument " 
     findMax(["name", " enam ", " game " ]) = = " enam " 
